        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Telekinetic Storm</em></p>\n<p>A beam of Force energy flashes out from your hand in a 5-foot-wide, 60-foot-long line. Each creature in the line must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 8d6 force damage and is knocked prone. On a successful save, it takes half as much damage and isn&rsquo;t knocked prone.</p>\n<p>You can create a new telekinetic gust as your action on your turn until the power ends.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Force Potency.</strong></em>&nbsp;When you cast this power using a force slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by 2d6 for each slot level above 6th.</p>",
